div.div: Lee Hojae had given up his life as a pro gamer, until one day he received a mysterious message: Congratulations! Youve been invited to the Tutorial World. Intrigued, he enters the game and confidently chooses hell difficulty, but soon learns that he is trapped there. With a mere 0.01% survival rate, Hojae must somehow overcome the games agonizing challenges to figure out the real reason he was invited. This tutorial may be tough, but its secrets are whats truly hellacious. (Source: Tapas)

Dungeons and monsters suddenly appear and the world falls into chaos. Ki-Bong Kim, an ordinary young part-timer, has been sucked up into an awakening dimension for 3000 years to train his powers. When he makes his return to reality, he is a max-leveled player who only has one wish -- to reconcile with his loved ones. 10 years have passed in the real world during his absence. How will Ki-Bong be able to find his place in the world with his new limit-breaking abilities?
(Source: WEBTOONS, edited)
